{"tid":463680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【五毛去咗邊？】僅20人撐國歌法 支持球迷要戴口罩","createTime":"2017-11-09T17:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T17:22:02.000Z","uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c6b3a3b86828af8b688c5d522eec3d3fb28f0443","tid":463680,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T17:22:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171109/large/1510232939_3717.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171109%2Flarge%2F1510232939_3717.jpg&h=f86fe3da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n賽前有消息指，警方因恐有支持國歌法的球迷入場，與部份球迷發生衝突，故警方加派人手到場以維持秩序。在現場所見，的確有為數約20名手持中國國旗與香港區旗的球迷到場，並被安排坐在東看台的觀眾席到場觀戰，而這批人士持中國國旗外全部穿紅色POLO SHIRT到場，並稱入場是支持中國及香港足球。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20171109/57439270\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171109%2F57439270&d=bh3RZ%2BlsTOrqm6zfbvEFy9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=962777e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171109%2F57439270&h=c5a93c41\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20171109/57439270</a>"}]}